column9: Lifetime: The number of people who had your Page's post enter their screen. Posts include statuses, photos, links, videos and more. (Unique Users)
column10: Lifetime: The number of people who had your Page's post enter their screen through unpaid distribution. (Unique Users)
column11: Lifetime: The number of people who had your Page's post enter their screen through paid distribution such as an ad. (Unique Users)
column12: Lifetime: The number of times your Page's post entered a person's screen. Posts include statuses, photos, links, videos and more. (Total Count)

column14: Lifetime: The number of times your Page's post entered a person's screen through paid distribution such as an ad. (Total Count)
column15: Lifetime: The number of unique people who engaged in certain ways with your Page post, for example by commenting on, liking, sharing, or clicking upon particular elements of the post. (Unique Users)

column3:
Episode 3 of #Futurewomen: THE QUEST is LIVE! Futurewomen is an alternate reality series about the creation of black superheroines!

In this episode we explore the stories of the characters in Honey Pot Performance's Ma(s)king Her, a dance-theater work of speculative fiction about empowered future beings and journeywomen
.#Afrofuturist #hpp2015 #weareopentv #opentv

The premiere of #Futurewomen Episode 3: THE QUEST goes LIVE tomorrow exclusively on OPEN TV - beta! 

In episode 2 we established the characters of Honey Pot Performance's Afrofuturist dance theater work, "Ma(s)king Her." 

Watch this episode to learn how they begin their journeys, with documentation from the first performances of the work at Links Hall! 

#Afrofuturist #hpp2015 #weareopentv #opentv
ALL of our friends are thriving! Congrats Honey Pot Performance, Darling Squire, Sofia Moreno and JRV MAJESTY Productions!! <3 <3 <3
Zackary Drucker's #OpenTVPresents pilot, #SouthernforPussy, will be screening at Columbia College's Glass Curtain Gallery this winter until February 2016! Opening reception is Thursday 5-8PM.

Next up in the #OpenTVOriginals vertical is #FullOutSeries! 

A story of ambition, manipulation, betrayal, and self-discovery, Full Out follows a closeted dancer as she struggles to regain her glory following a devastating injury. 

Catch the official trailer below. Premiering exclusively on #OpenTV in 2016. #weareopentv #lesbian King is a Fink Productions
